---
title: Roasted Spring Asparagus Serves 4 | with Lemony Tarragon Cream Sauce
description: It's asparagus season! These tender and bright spring veggies get a boost of flavour from a simple lemony tarragon cream sauce. The perfect veggie side dish to accompany any meal!
